Accep a number 'n'.
 If the n > 10 Display "Too big a number" and Stop
    Else if n < 0 Display "Negative Number" and Stop
    Else go to Step-04.
Repeat the steps 05 & 06 until ( n < 0 ).  Initialize fact to 1.
 fact = fact * n 
 Decrement n.
 Repeat the steps 08 & 09 until (fact < 0). Initialize sum to 0
sum = sum + fact % 10.
 fact = fact / 10
Display sum
